articles.author: Byron Kaye, Renju Jose
articles.title: Australia supermarkets should face hefty fines for code of conduct breach, says report - Reuters
articles.description: Australia's major supermarkets should face hefty fines if they do not comply with an industry code of conduct when dealing with suppliers, a government-commissioned report said while rejecting calls to give regulators the power to break up the big chains.

articles.author: Sarah Perez
articles.title: Spotify launches personalized AI playlists that you can build using prompts - TechCrunch
articles.description: AI playlists will initially become available to users on Android and iOS devices in the U.K. and Australia and will be iterated on in the months ahead.
